data.description: PRICE REDUCED!This pristine, MOVE IN READY, 4 bedrooms, 3 bath home is loaded with hardwood flooring throughout the 1st floor, crown molding, large kitchen island with granite counter tops &tile back splash, tile shower with bench seat in Master, gas fireplace, tankless water heater and closets galore is the home you’ve been searching for. This beautiful Madison city home is conveniently located within minutes to County Line Rd, I-565, Toyota Field, the Amazon, Mazda, & Toyota plants, and the Huntsville Intl Airport.
